(412, 4, '2016-03-06 09:13:52', '2016-03-06 14:13:52', 'Au Québec du 7 au 13 mars, c''est la semaine du Mac and Cheese. Des tonnes de restaurants se prêteront au jeu pour offrir aux clients des plats de macaronis au fromage des plus savoureux. Fini le traditionnel macaroni au fromage, tout collant ou trop liquide, qui manque de punch!\n\nPour honorer cette merveilleuse semaine, je vous ai déniché de décadentes recettes de Mac and Cheese. Le Kraft dinner avec des saucisses à hot-dog? Y''a rien là!!!\n\nLa question est; lesquels seriez-vous prêts à manger?\n\nMais surtout, lesquels seriez-vous prêt à en assumer tous les effets...? ??\n\n<strong><span style="color: #ff9900">1.  Le Hot-dog au Mac and Cheese</span></strong>\n\n<span style="color: #ff9900">(Mayo et ketchup, why not tant qu''à y être!)</span>\n\n<a href="http://localhost/lepatechinois/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/img_2200.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-416" src="http://localhost/lepatechinois/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/img_2200.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="640" /></a>\n\n<strong><span style="color: #ff9900">2. Le lobster au Mac and Cheese!</span></strong>\n\n<span style="color: #ff9900">(Les petits pois c''est pour la culpabilité c''est ça?)</span>\n\n<a href="http://localhost/lepatechinois/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/img_2208.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-417" src="http://localhost/lepatechinois/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/img_2208.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="640" /></a>\n\n<strong><span style="color: #ff9900">3. Le burger au Mac and Cheese ...</span></strong>\n\n<span style="color: #ff9900">(un gros OUI!)</span>\n\n<a href="http://localhost/lepatechinois/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/img_2212.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-419" src="http://localhost/lepatechinois/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/img_2212.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="640" /></a>\n\n<span style="color: #ff9900"><strong>4. Le panini pulled pork et Mac and Cheese</strong></span>\n\n<a href="http://localhost/lepatechinois/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/img_2217.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-418" src="http://localhost/lepatechinois/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/img_2217.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="640" /></a>\n\n<strong><span style="color: #ff9900">5. La pizza Mac and Cheese</span></strong>\n\n<span style="color: #ff9900">(Enfin une pizza qui ne manquera pas de fromage! Pas de charcuterie en plus, c''est super santé!)</span>\n\n<a href="http://localhost/lepatechinois/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/img_2214.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-420" src="http://localhost/lepatechinois/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/img_2214.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="640" /></a>\n\n<span style="color: #ff9900"><strong>6. La casserole de Mac and Cheese, croutons et bacon </strong></span>\n\n<a href="http://localhost/lepatechinois/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/img_2215-e1463754260791.jpg"><img class="alignnone wp-image-421 size-full" src="http://localhost/lepatechinois/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/img_2215-e1463754260791.jpg" width="624" height="435" /></a>\n\n<strong><span style="color: #ff9900">7. Un autre genre de burger Mac and Cheese</span></strong>\n\n<span style="color: #ff9900">(C''est encore un OUI)</span>\n\n<a href="http://localhost/lepatechinois/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/img_2218.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-422" src="http://localhost/lepatechinois/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/img_2218.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="640" /></a>\n\n<strong><span style="color: #ff9900">8. Grilled Cheese, Mac and Cheese et Bacon</span></strong>\n\n<span style="color: #ff9900">(Ha et épinards!!!)</span>\n\n<a href="http://localhost/lepatechinois/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/img_2219.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-423" src="http://localhost/lepatechinois/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/img_2219.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="640" /></a>\n\n<strong><span style="color: #ff9900">9. Mais quelle merveilleuse idée! Mac and Cheese et Brownie aux Oreos. Le repas parfait !!!</span></strong>\n\n<a href="http://localhost/lepatechinois/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/img_2223.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-424" src="http://localhost/lepatechinois/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/img_2223.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="640" /></a>\n\n<span style="color: #ff9900"><strong>10. Panini au poulet frit et Mac and Cheese</strong></span>\n\n<a href="http://localhost/lepatechinois/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/img_2222.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-426" src="http://localhost/lepatechinois/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/img_2222.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="640" /></a>\n\n<span style="color: #ff9900"><strong>11. Petites boules d''amour de Mac and Cheese, enrobées de bacon</strong></span>\n\n<a href="http://localhost/lepatechinois/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/img_2224.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-425" src="http://localhost/lepatechinois/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/img_2224.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="640" /></a>\n\n<strong><span style="color: #ff9900">12. Le Mac and Cheese à la Pizza</span></strong>\n\n<a href="http://localhost/lepatechinois/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/img_2225.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-427" src="http://localhost/lepatechinois/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/img_2225.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="640" /></a>\n\n<span style="color: #ff9900"><strong>13. Sandwich de poulet frit, patates pilées, sauce brune et... Mac and Cheese!</strong></span>\n\n<a href="http://localhost/lepatechinois/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/img_2229.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-428" src="http://localhost/lepatechinois/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/img_2229.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="640" /></a>\n\n<span style="color: #ff9900"><strong>14. Le Mac and Cheese au homard</strong></span>\n\n<a href="http://localhost/lepatechinois/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/img_2228.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-429" src="http://localhost/lepatechinois/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/img_2228.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="640" /></a>\n\n<strong><span style="color: #ff9900">15. Un autre burger (bon ok plus qu''un) avec du poulet frit et du Mac and Cheese</span></strong>\n\n<span style="color: #ff9900">(Celui là c''est non...)</span>\n\n<a href="http://localhost/lepatechinois/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/img_2227.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-430" src="http://localhost/lepatechinois/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/img_2227.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="640" /></a>\n\n<span style="color: #ff9900"><strong>16. Mac and Cheese... cheese cake!</strong></span>\n\n<a href="http://localhost/lepatechinois/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/img_2226.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-431" src="http://localhost/lepatechinois/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/img_2226.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="640" /></a>\n\n<strong><span style="color: #ff9900">17. Le tortillas Mac and Cheese, avocat et crevettes épicées</span></strong>\n\n<span style="color: #ff9900">(Mmmmm)</span>\n\n<a href="http://localhost/lepatechinois/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/img_2231.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-437" src="http://localhost/lepatechinois/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/img_2231.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="640" /></a>\n\n<span style="color: #ff9900"><strong>18. Je ne sais pas comment décrire celui-là...</strong></span>\n\n<a href="http://localhost/lepatechinois/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/img_2233.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-432" src="http://localhost/lepatechinois/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/img_2233.jpg" alt="" width="320" height="320" /></a>\n\n<strong><span style="color: #ff9900">19. Aile de poulet farcie au Mac and Cheese</span></strong>\n\n<a href="http://localhost/lepatechinois/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/img_2237.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-433" src="http://localhost/lepatechinois/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/img_2237.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="640" /></a>\n\n<span style="color: #ff9900"><strong>20. Mac and Cheese dans un bol de pain</strong></span>\n\n<a href="http://localhost/lepatechinois/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/img_2236.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-435" src="http://localhost/lepatechinois/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/img_2236.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="640" /></a>\n\n<strong><span style="color: #ff9900">21. Le Mac and Cheese au Cheetos épicés</span></strong>\n\n<a href="http://localhost/lepatechinois/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/img_2234.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-436" src="http://localhost/lepatechinois/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/img_2234.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="640" /></a>\n\n<strong><span style="color: #ff9900">22. Le dernier c''est pour aider votre digestion</span></strong>\n\n<span style="color: #ff9900">(J''ose espérer qu''à droite ce sont des cantaloup et non des petites patates...)</span>\n\n<img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-441" src="http://localhost/lepatechinois/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/IMG_2230-300x300.jpg" alt="IMG_2230" width="300" height="300" />', 'Semaine du Mac n Cheese;  10 lbs de plus juste en regardant ces recettes ??', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'semaine-du-mac-n-cheese-10-lbs-de-plus-juste-en-regardant-ces-recettes-%f0%9f%90%b7%f0%9f%98%8f', '', '', '2016-03-06 09:13:52', '2016-03-06 14:13:52', '', 0, 'http://lepatechinois.com/?p=412', 0, 'post', '', 0),
